page_title: Guess Women's Gold Crystal Dial Gold Tone Steel Mesh Bracelet GW0550L2 - First Class Watches™
meta_description: Guess GW0550L2 - . Guess first began as a denim brand with its first shop opening in Beverly Hills. The brand was founded by brothers Paul and Maurice Marciano. The brand&rsquo;s success came very quickly, and Guess jeans had become some of the most popular in the world by the 1980s. Guess began producing watches in 1983 and created a range of styles for men and women at an affordable price. The watches have a sleek, elegant style that can be easily styled for any occasion. Core Features of a Guess Watch: Guess watches are available in a&nbsp;range of styles and designs&nbsp;to ensure that there is a perfect model for every collector. The watches are created using precise and reliable&nbsp;battery powered quartz movements.&nbsp;&nbsp; Each Guess watch has a level of&nbsp;water resistance&nbsp;that makes them suitable for daily wear. Model Specifications GW0550L1: This model features a&nbsp;gold crystal-set dial&nbsp;that is surrounded by&nbsp;concentric crystal-set circles.&nbsp; The dial exhibits&nbsp;gold&nbsp;hour, minute and second hands.&nbsp; A&nbsp;crystal-set gold-tone stainless steel case&nbsp;frames the dial. The case measures&nbsp;36mm in diameter. The watch is finished with a&nbsp;gold-tone&nbsp;stainless steel mesh bracelet. This model is&nbsp;splash resistant and should not be submerged in water.&nbsp; . Official Guess UK retailer. The Guess GW0550L2 comes with free delivery, 2 year guarantee, 30 day returns and box.

product_info.description:
Guess first began as a denim brand with its first shop opening in Beverly Hills. The brand was founded by brothers Paul and Maurice Marciano. The brand’s success came very quickly, and Guess jeans had become some of the most popular in the world by the 1980s. Guess began producing watches in 1983 and created a range of styles for men and women at an affordable price. The watches have a sleek, elegant style that can be easily styled for any occasion.

Core Features of a Guess Watch:

  • Guess watches are available in a range of styles and designs to ensure that there is a perfect model for every collector.
  • The watches are created using precise and reliable battery powered quartz movements.  
  • Each Guess watch has a level of water resistance that makes them suitable for daily wear.

Model Specifications GW0550L1:

  • This model features a gold crystal-set dial that is surrounded by concentric crystal-set circles. 
  • The dial exhibits gold hour, minute and second hands. 
  • A crystal-set gold-tone stainless steel case frames the dial. The case measures 36mm in diameter.
  • The watch is finished with a gold-tone stainless steel mesh bracelet.
  • This model is splash resistant and should not be submerged in water.
